                            <comment id="84930" author="huntc" created="Wed, 7 Nov 2012 12:38:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Rossen - I did search for an existing issue first and couldn&apos;t find one - we&apos;re on M2 so I&apos;ll see that we upgrade to RC1 asap.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
